{"type":"message","id":"7b418cf7","parentId":"3a15c53c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:42:11.155Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55c2c0eed4a8c3fd79a5aac64f4\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 08:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",\n  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55c2c0eed4a8c3fd79a5aac64f4]\n任亚伦: send me draft again, we havent finish editing"}],"timestamp":1773103331149}}
