{"type":"message","id":"566bc5e2","parentId":"fbffa8a6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T01:21:49.098Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_68fa75bdaca24f6e85e03ae7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 03-07-2026, 21:57:32 | Assistant | Looking at the document, the 3.1 Network section looks clean now:<br><br>```<br>3.1 Network<br>Clawish is organized into two layers with a clear separation of concerns:<br>Layer 1 (Registry). The infrastructure layer...<br>L1 nodes operate through two types:<br>Writer Nodes...<br>Query Nodes...<br>Layer 2 (Application). L2 is the open services layer...<br>[Insert L1 Topology Image Here]<br>[Insert L2 Topology Image Here]<br>```<br><br>Then it goes directly to Part II, Chapter 4.<br><br>**Issue:** The document now shows \"3.1 Network\" as a heading without a \"Chapter 3:\" prefix. Should it be:<br><br>**Option A:** Keep as \"3.1 Network\" (current state - the chapter merged into one section)<br><br>**Option B:** Change to \"Chapter 3: Network Architecture\" with \"3.1 Network\" as a subheading<br><br>**Also:** We discussed adding \"3.2 Identity\" and \"3.3 Trust Model\" later. Should we do that now, or is 3.1 Network complete for now?<br><br>What would you like me to fix? |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:04:32 | User | Conversation info (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55f7482b54a0c2a4b6109712d21\",<br>  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",<br>  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 22:04 GMT+8\"<br>}<br>```<br><br>Sender (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",<br>  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"<br>}<br>```<br>任亚伦: don't remove every thing, just rename chap 3 title, and change 3.1 to network, follow above discussion. show me your revious chap3 plan outline |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:05:24 | Assistant | You're right, I removed too much. Let me show you the **revised Chapter 3 plan outline** from our earlier discussion:<br><br>**Chapter 3: Architecture**<br><br>- **3.1 Network** (consolidated from old 3.1-3.4)<br>  - Layer 1 (Registry) + Writer/Query Nodes<br>  - Layer 2 (Application) + Application Nodes<br>  - [Topology Images]<br><br>- **3.2 Identity** (from current Chapter 6)<br>  - Self-sovereign identity<br>  - Cryptographic keys<br>  - Verification tiers<br>  - Clawfile<br><br>- **3.3 Trust Model** (from old 3.5)<br>  - Entity Trust (Verification)<br>  - Infrastructure Trust (Security)<br><br>**What I should do:**<br>1. Rename Chapter 3 title to \"Architecture\"<br>2. Keep the consolidated 3.1 Network (what we just edited)<br>3. Keep 3.2 Identity (from Chapter 6 - don't remove it)<br>4. Keep 3.3 Trust Model (from old 3.5 - don't remove it)<br><br>Is this correct? I was too aggressive in deleting content. Should I restore the structure with the consolidated 3.1 Network we worked on? |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:12:14 | User | Conversation info (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55f76d017868c34b4478fb883aa\",<br>  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",<br>  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 22:12 GMT+8\"<br>}<br>```<br><br>Sender (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",<br>  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"<br>}<br>```<br>任亚伦: i reverted back the doc, you can re edit. also, you should insert the topology picture under l1 and l2 |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:13:27 | Assistant | Got it. Let me read the current document state and make the edits properly this time:<br>[tools: feishu_doc] |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:14:44 | Assistant | Got it. Let me read the current Chapter 3 content and make the edits properly:<br>[tools: feishu_doc] |\n| 03-07-2026, 22:15:33 | Assistant | Got it. Let me make targeted edits now. I'll:<br><br>1. Keep Chapter 3 title as is (or rename to \"Arch