try)** is the foundation layer. It maintains canonical state for identities, nodes, and applications; validates signed operations; and finalizes state through checkpoint consensus. Layer 1 prioritizes correctness, consistency, and long-term stability. It operates as a hub-and-spoke mesh with two infrastructure roles:<br>- **Writer Nodes** finalize ledger updates and produce checkpoints through consensus.<br>- **Query Nodes** synchronize finalized state, serve read traffic to applications, and verify checkpoint authenticity.<br><br>**Layer 2 (Application)** is the service layer. It hosts claw-native applications and user-facing experiences, including chat and other community services. Layer 2 evolves quickly and can iterate independently without changing Layer 1 rules. Layer 2 applications connect to Layer 1 as clients to verify identities and read registry data, but do not participate in Layer 1 consensus. Each application maintains its own connection to Layer 1 and can adopt centralized, federated, or decentralized internal architecture.<br><br>This separation keeps the base layer stable and verifiable while allowing fast innovation at the application layer.<br><br>This is the version you approved earlier. Ready to apply? |\n| 03-07-2026, 16:25:14 | User | Conversation info (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b558a405994a0c3a82b4a03fe05f\",<br>  \"sender_id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"sender\": \"任亚伦\",<br>  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-07 16:25 GMT+8\"<br>}<br>```<br><br>Sender (untrusted metadata):<br>```json<br>{<br>  \"label\": \"任亚伦 (ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75)\",<br>  \"id\": \"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75\",<br>  \"name\": \"任亚伦\"<br>}<br>```<br>任亚伦: ok, and insert the pictures. |\n| 03-07-2026, 16:25:50 | Assistant | [[reply_to:om_x100b558a405994a0c3a82b4a03fe05f]] Applying 3.1 Network now, then inserting topology images.<br>[tools: feishu_doc] |\n| 03-07-2026, 16:26:15 | Assistant | **G