{"type":"message","id":"d45c9f6f","parentId":"4806e98e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:42:45.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Fixed the \"Application nodes\" → \"Applications\" in 3.1 Network section. The L1 and L2 naming is now consistent:\n- L1 = Nodes (Registry layer)\n- L2 = Apps (Application layer)","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Fixed. Now consistent:\n\n| Layer | What | Title |\n|-------|------|-------|\n| **L1** | Nodes | Layer 1 (Registry) ✅ |\n| **L2** | Apps | Layer 2 (Application) ✅ |\n\nChanged \"Application nodes\" → \"Applications\" in the description."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":123744,"output":139,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123883,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773110530685}}
