{"type":"message","id":"c9d4972e","parentId":"22f5073c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:08:10.892Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add left padding. The current viewBox is 820 width. I should add padding on the left. Let me adjust the viewBox and shift all elements to the right.\n\nActually, a simpler approach is to just widen the viewBox and shift the content. Let me think about the current positioning:\n- App1 starts at x=5\n- All Writers ends at x=550+230=780\n\nIf I increase the viewBox width to 820 and want even padding on both sides, I should shift everything right by about 20 pixels.\n\nLet me change the viewBox to start at -20 or increase width and shift content. Actually, the easier way is to adjust the viewBox x-start to be negative.\n\nLet me just make viewBox wider: from \"0 0 820 380\" to \"-20 0 860 380\" which adds 20px on each side.\n\nOr simpler: I can adjust the viewBox to be \"0 0 860 380\" and then shift all x coordinates by 20. But that's a lot of changes.\n\nActually, the simplest is to change viewBox to \"-20 0 840 380\" which adds 20px padding on left and keeps the right side the same.\n\nWait, that won't add padding on the right. Let me think again.\n\nCurrent: viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\"\nContent spans roughly from x=5 to x=780\n\nTo add 20px padding on each side:\n- viewBox should be \"0 0 860 380\" (total width 860)\n- All x coordinates shift by +20\n\nActually, easier approach: just change viewBox to \"-20 0 860 380\"\n- This adds 20px on left (negative start)\n- And 20px on right (860 - 780 = 80, minus the original 40 = 40... hmm this is confusing)\n\nLet me just shift all the x values by 20 and keep viewBox at 820. Actually, I already widened to 820. Let me shift content right by adding a transform or adjusting viewBox.\n\nSimplest: viewBox=\"-20 0 860 380\" \n- Left padding: 20px (from -20 to 0)\n- Right padding: 860 - 780 = 80px... that's more than needed\n\nActually let me just check what makes sense:\n- Original viewBox: 780\n- Current: 820\n- I want even padding\n\nLet me use viewBox=\"-10 0 830 380\" which gives:\n- 10px left padding\n- 830 - 780 = 50px on right\n- Still not even\n\nLet me just shift all the content by adjusting the x coordinates. That's the cleanest way.\n\nActually, looking at the SVG, the leftmost element starts at x=5 (the App1 rect). If I want 20px padding on left, everything needs to shift right by 20. Then viewBox should be 820 with content from x=25 to x=800.\n\nBut this requires changing many x coordinates. Let me use a transform instead.\n\nActually, the easiest is to add a group with transform=\"translate(20, 0)\" around all the content, and increase viewBox width to 840.\n\nLet me try that approach.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6dbb92c1c4154e29b2d27759","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/writer-merge-process.svg"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":129634,"output":1042,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130676,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773112068538}}
{"type":"message","id":"c308c2df","parentId":"c9d4972e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:08:10.921Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6dbb92c1c4154e29b2d27759","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<svg viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <defs>\n    <style>\n      .title { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; fill: #333; }\n      .label { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 10px; fill: #fff; font-weight: 600; }\n      .oplabel { font-family: monospace; font-size: 9px; fill: #fff; }\n      .stagelabel { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; fill: #666; font-weight: 500; }\n      .writername { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; fill: #555; font-weight: 600; }\n      .time { font-family: monospace; font-size: 9px; fill: #fff; font-weight: 500; }\n      .dots { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; fill: #666; font-weight: 600; }\n      .l2label { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; font-size: 12px; fill: #555; font-weight: 600; }\n    </style>\n    <marker id=\"arrow\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"7\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <polygon points=\"0 0, 8 3, 0 6\" fill=\"#888\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n  \n  <!-- Title -->\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"25\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"title\">Multi-Writer Merge Process</text>\n  \n  <!-- L2 Applications Label -->\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"55\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"stagelabel\">L2 Applications</text>\n  \n  <!-- L1 Nodes Label - between writers and all writers columns -->\n  <text x=\"510\" y=\"55\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"stagelabel\">L1 Nodes</text>\n  \n  <!-- App1 (Actor A) - has two operations: t1 and t2 with even vertical spacing -->\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"l2label\">App1</text>\n  <rect x=\"5\" y=\"90\" width=\"160\" height=\"100\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#ecfdf5\" stroke=\"#10b981\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"15\" y=\"102\" width=\"140\" height=\"32\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#34d399\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"123\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t1: key.register</text>\n  <rect x=\"15\" y=\"145\" width=\"140\" height=\"32\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#34d399\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"166\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\" font-size=\"9\">t2: key.rotate</text>\n  \n  <!-- App2 (Actor B) - has one operation: t3 -->\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"l2label\">App2</text>\n  <rect x=\"5\" y=\"218\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#ecfdf5\" stroke=\"#10b981\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"15\" y=\"230\" width=\"140\" height=\"28\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#34d399\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"249\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t3: profile.update</text>\n  \n  <!-- App3 (Actor C) - has one operation: t4 -->\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"290\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"l2label\">App3</text>\n  <rect x=\"5\" y=\"298\" width=\"160\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#ecfdf5\" stroke=\"#10b981\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"15\" y=\"310\" width=\"140\" height=\"28\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#34d399\"/>\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"329\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t4: ledger.entry</text>\n  \n  <!-- Dots below apps -->\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"365\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dots\">...</text>\n  \n  <!-- Arrows from Apps to Writers -->\n  <!-- App1 (Actor A) has TWO lines: t1 to Writer 1, t2 to Writer 2 -->\n  <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"118\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"145\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"161\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"265\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  \n  <!-- App2 (Actor B) to Writer 1 -->\n  <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"244\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"195\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  \n  <!-- App3 (Actor C) to Writer 2 -->\n  <line x1=\"165\" y1=\"324\" x2=\"270\" y2=\"315\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.2\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Writer 1 - Blue -->\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"writername\">Writer 1</text>\n  <rect x=\"270\" y=\"90\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#eff6ff\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"280\" y=\"102\" width=\"160\" height=\"42\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#60a5fa\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"128\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t1: key.register</text>\n  <rect x=\"280\" y=\"155\" width=\"160\" height=\"42\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#60a5fa\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"181\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t3: profile.update</text>\n  \n  <!-- Writer 2 - Blue -->\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"writername\">Writer 2</text>\n  <rect x=\"270\" y=\"238\" width=\"180\" height=\"120\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#eff6ff\" stroke=\"#3b82f6\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <rect x=\"280\" y=\"250\" width=\"160\" height=\"42\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#60a5fa\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"276\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t2: key.rotate</text>\n  <rect x=\"280\" y=\"303\" width=\"160\" height=\"42\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#60a5fa\"/>\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"329\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t4: ledger.entry</text>\n  \n  <!-- Curved arrows pointing to vertical center of All Writers (y=225) -->\n  <path d=\"M 450 150 C 490 150, 510 225, 550 225\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\n  <path d=\"M 450 298 C 490 298, 510 225, 550 225\" stroke=\"#888\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" fill=\"none\"/>\n  \n  <!-- Dots after Writer 2 -->\n  <text x=\"360\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dots\">...</text>\n  \n  <!-- Unified Result -->\n  <text x=\"660\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"writername\">All Writers</text>\n  <rect x=\"550\" y=\"90\" width=\"230\" height=\"270\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#f0f7ff\" stroke=\"#4a90d9\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"115\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"stagelabel\" fill=\"#4a90d9\">Sorted by Timestamp</text>\n  \n  <!-- 4 operations sorted by time - no actor labels -->\n  <rect x=\"562\" y=\"130\" width=\"206\" height=\"40\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#4a90d9\"/>\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"155\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t1: key.register</text>\n  \n  <rect x=\"562\" y=\"180\" width=\"206\" height=\"40\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#4a90d9\"/>\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t2: key.rotate</text>\n  \n  <rect x=\"562\" y=\"230\" width=\"206\" height=\"40\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#4a90d9\"/>\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t3: profile.update</text>\n  \n  <rect x=\"562\" y=\"280\" width=\"206\" height=\"40\" rx=\"3\" fill=\"#4a90d9\"/>\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"305\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"label\">t4: ledger.entry</text>\n  \n  <!-- Dots at bottom of merged checkpoint -->\n  <text x=\"665\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dots\">...</text>\n</svg>\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773112090906}}
{"type":"message","id":"399f0b49","parentId":"c308c2df","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:08:39.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to:\n1. Add left padding to balance with right padding\n2. Already changed \"L2 Apps\" to \"L2 Applications\"\n\nCurrent viewBox is \"0 0 820 380\"\n- Leftmost element starts at x=5\n- Rightmost element ends at x=550+230=780\n\nTo add even padding:\n- Left padding: currently 5px, want ~20px\n- Right padding: currently 820-780=40px\n\nSo I need to shift everything right by about 15-20px to make left padding match right padding (around 40px each).\n\nLet me change viewBox to \"-20 0 860 380\" which would give:\n- Left: content starts at x=5, so padding from -20 to 5 = 25px\n- Right: content ends at 780, so padding from 780 to 860 = 80px... that's too much\n\nActually, let me just shift content by adjusting viewBox. The simplest approach:\n\nviewBox=\"-35 0 820 380\" would give:\n- Left padding: 35 + 5 = 40px (from viewBox start -35 to content start at 5)\n- Right padding: 820 - 780 = 40px\n\nWait, that's not how viewBox works. viewBox=\"-35 0 820 380\" means:\n- x starts at -35\n- width is 820\n- So x ranges from -35 to 785\n- Content starts at x=5, so left padding = 5 - (-35) = 40px\n- Content ends at x=780, right padding = 785 - 780 = 5px... no that's wrong\n\nActually viewBox=\"-35 0 820 380\" means:\n- x from -35 to 785\n- The rendered image starts at x=-35\n\nSo if content is from x=5 to x=780:\n- Left padding: 5 - (-35) = 40px ✗ wrong, the viewBox starting at -35 means we SEE from -35\n\nHmm, let me think again. viewBox=\"x y width height\" defines the rectangle to show.\n- viewBox=\"-35 0 820 380\" shows x from -35 to 785\n- Content from x=5 to x=780\n- Left visible padding: from -35 to 5 = 40px\n- Right visible padding: from 780 to 785 = 5px\n\nThat's not what I want. I want even padding.\n\nCurrent: viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\"\n- Content from 5 to 780\n- Left padding: 5px\n- Right padding: 820 - 780 = 40px\n\nTo make even padding of 20px each:\n- viewBox=\"0 0 800 380\"\n- Content from 5 to 780\n- Left padding: 5px\n- Right padding: 800 - 780 = 20px\n\nStill not even.\n\nBetter: shift content right by 35px, then viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\" gives:\n- Content from 40 to 815\n- Left padding: 40px\n- Right padding: 820 - 815 = 5px... still wrong\n\nLet me try: shift content right by 17px, viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\"\n- Content from 22 to 797\n- Left padding: 22px\n- Right padding: 820 - 797 = 23px\n\nThat's close to even!\n\nBut shifting content requires changing many x values. Let me use transform.\n\nActually, the easiest is to use viewBox that starts negative and extends width:\nviewBox=\"-17 0 820 380\" shows from -17 to 803\n- Content from 5 to 780\n- Left padding: 5 - (-17) = 22px\n- Right padding: 803 - 780 = 23px\n\nThat's almost even!\n\nLet me try viewBox=\"-18 0 822 380\":\n- Shows from -18 to 804\n- Content from 5 to 780\n- Left padding: 5 - (-18) = 23px\n- Right padding: 804 - 780 = 24px\n\nEven better! Let me use viewBox=\"-20 0 825 380\":\n- Shows from -20 to 805\n- Content from 5 to 780\n- Left padding: 25px\n- Right padding: 805 - 780 = 25px\n\nThis gives exactly even 25px padding on both sides.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_80ab67bbd0a4411bb83d8267","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/writer-merge-process.svg","newText":"<svg viewBox=\"-20 0 825 380\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">","oldText":"<svg viewBox=\"0 0 820 380\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":124542,"output":1482,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126024,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773112090921}}
