{"type":"message","id":"2251fbee","parentId":"1cf6c259","timestamp":"2026-03-10T05:02:49.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Section 3.1 Network now flows:\n1. Layer 1 (Nodes) - what it is\n2. L1 Node Functions - what nodes do\n3. Node types (Writer Nodes, Query Nodes)\n4. Layer 1 diagram\n5. Layer 2 (Application)\n6. Layer 2 diagram\n\nThis is a better flow: purpose → functions → types.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Done. 3.1 Network now flows:\n\n1. **Layer 1 (Nodes)** — what it is\n2. **L1 Node Functions** — what nodes do\n3. **Node types** — Writers, Queries\n4. **Layer 1 diagram**\n5. **Layer 2 (Application)** — what it is\n6. **Layer 2 diagram**\n\nBetter flow: purpose → functions → types."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":116343,"output":203,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116546,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773118921726}}
