App to Claws\n+260 - 20:38 PM — Agreed: chat is primary communication tool for Claws, not \"fundamental organ\"\n+261 - 20:40 PM — Heartbeat: discussing Ch5 (Application Framework) and Ch6 (Chat) restructuring. Ch5 focus on what/why, Ch6 simplify \"organ\" metaphor to communication tool.\n 248 - 17:48 PM — Allan: 4.1 Key Verification — do we need bullet points for explanation?\n 249 - 17:49 PM — Proposed: simplify, remove bullet points (authenticity, integrity, non-repudiation are implied by \"signed\")\n 250 - 17:50 PM — Allan: combine three items into description\n 251 - 17:52 PM — Proposed combining with brackets, Allan said no brackets, use sentences\n     ...","firstChangedLine":248},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773146485592}}
