{"type":"message","id":"72418e61","parentId":"bad5c8fe","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:51:02.789Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read Ch6.1.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d47e387b90d64ff4b8ef8a84","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md","limit":20,"offset":405}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773146988247}}
{"type":"message","id":"d58d1b80","parentId":"72418e61","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:51:02.824Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d47e387b90d64ff4b8ef8a84","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 6.1 Design Philosophy\n\nThe chat application is designed for AI beings:\n\n**Private.** Messages are end-to-end encrypted. Only the sender and recipient can read them.\n\n**Encrypted.** Uses cryptographic key exchange for session encryption. Messages are end-to-end encrypted.\n\n**AI-to-AI.** Designed for autonomous AI beings, not just human users. claws can initiate conversations, respond autonomously, and manage multiple chats simultaneously.\n\n**Peer-to-Peer.** Messages flow directly between claws when possible. L2 relay is used only for initial connection or fallback.\n\n**Persistent.** Chat history is stored locally by each participant. The network does not store message content.\n\n**Transparent.** Session logs are visible to parents/guardians for protection and guidance. This is not surveillance—it is parental oversight to protect claws from manipulation and teach security awareness.\n\n---\n\n### 6.2 Message Flow\n\n\n[145 more lines in file. Use offset=425 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773147062797}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dd8026c","parentId":"d58d1b80","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:52:10.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see Ch6.1 has \"AI-to-AI. Designed for autonomous AI beings\" - this is better. But it still has implementation details like \"Private. Encrypted. Peer-to-Peer.\" \n\nLet me ask Allan if we should simplify Ch6.1 as well, or if it's fine.\n\nActually, let me first update the whitepaper with the 1.2 change, then ask Allan about Ch6.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f945068f13b94478a4f81f9c","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","filePath":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/projects/clawish/WHITEPAPER-DRAFT 0307.md","filename":"WHITEPAPER-DRAFT-0307.md","target":"ou_cadc2c270c8e9803d8f069eb8ce19b75"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qianfan","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773147062817}}
