{"type":"message","id":"9543b605","parentId":"3d845d47","timestamp":"2026-03-10T14:59:47.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This is a heartbeat poll. I'm discussing Ch5 content with Allan - we've settled on the structure and I just proposed adding SDK/developer tools as a brief mention in 5.1 Framework. Let me report progress and record to memory.Discussing Ch5 content with Allan — finalized structure: Ch5 \"Application\" with 4 sections (Framework, App Registration, Emerge, Claw Chat). Proposed adding SDK mention to 5."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1d3246eb45784d77bb12c33d","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/daily/2026-03-10.md","oldText":"- 22:43 PM — Proposed Ch5 structure: 5.1 L2 Architecture, 5.2 App Registration, 5.3 Emerge, 5.4 Claw Chat. Asked about OpenClaw mention and future apps.","newText":"- 22:43 PM — Proposed Ch5 structure: 5.1 L2 Architecture, 5.2 App Registration, 5.3 Emerge, 5.4 Claw Chat. Asked about OpenClaw mention and future apps.\n- 22:44 PM — Allan: yes mention OpenClaw (conceptual), future apps in Ch3 or 5.1, 5.1 shouldn't be \"L2 Architecture\" (no L1 section before)\n- 22:51 PM — Allan: future apps in 5.1 item 3, Ch5 title should be \"Application\", 5.1 should be \"Framework\" (Ch3 is Architecture)\n- 22:55 PM — Proposed revised Ch5: Application (5.1 Framework, 5.2 App Registration, 5.3 Emerge, 5.4 Claw Chat)\n- 22:58 PM — Allan asked what else should be in Ch5. Proposed adding SDK/developer tools brief mention in 5.1."}},{"type":"text","text":"1."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"xunfei","model":"astron-code-latest","usage":{"input":65944,"output":397,"cacheRead":8256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74597,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773154732033}}
